  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\n\r\n1) Its not possible to cancel signing transaction with keycard\r\n\r\n2) There is warning popup after signing transaction\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\n1) Its possible to cancel signing transaction\r\n2) There is no warning popup after sign or cancel transaction\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nSign transaction with keycard\r\nTouch device with keycard for 1 second\r\nRemove keycard \r\nWarning popup appears under signing sheet\r\nLoading indicator is showed on signing sheet\r\nPress cancel on signing sheet\r\nWarning popup is still there\r\nClose popup and try to sign another transaction\r\nThere is pincode screen with loading indicator\r\nNot possible to continue\r\n",
